{"tid":1999691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"揸住李文亮單嘢根本上就已經夠唔明點解要兜一大個圈去查 其他嘢， 口同鼻拗","createTime":"2020-05-03T10:48:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T11:08:11.000Z","uid":185416,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f8e6fb4a8b28893dcbe208505820c6db19c7cf22","tid":1999691,"uid":185416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:48:14.000Z","msg":"李文亮單嘢全世界看在眼裏<br />\n係支那人將講真話嘅人滅聲<br />\n任由春運發生先會好似而家咁<br />\n<br />\n淨係呢單嘢已經可以charge支那係人禍， 唔係天災<br />\n根本上中國共產黨唔會辯駁到<br />\n<br />\n唔明點解要兜一大個圈去查係唔係p4實驗室流出嚟<br />\n即使查到都好容易反駁<br />\n到時就口同鼻拗<br />\n你吹佢唔脹<br />\n<br />\n根本上就要上twitter推李文亮單野等全球追討支那， 因為呢單嘢係證據確鑿， 冇得抵賴<br />\n而唔係查病毒來源<br />\n如果查到個病毒來源個病毒真係唔係呢支支， 到時翻牆內人又會打曬飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"860ce2f3a6a7bb05483b10b77ab22da67623c71d","tid":1999691,"uid":185416,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:49:04.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n上twitter la"},{"pid":"a92a535949d6d00e588b1eaa7e160a0b6f46e1a1","tid":1999691,"uid":185416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:50:52.000Z","msg":"李文亮"},{"pid":"e2bd6a7840d64f91b0b7d071439d8e531ac43190","tid":1999691,"uid":185416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:51:03.000Z","msg":"李文亮"},{"pid":"6e57bd9dc16952a502a119e8ed9b50b5ddcc9f0b","tid":1999691,"uid":82394,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:51:40.000Z","msg":"咪就係"},{"pid":"ee9752e97d3e6c103701cf237123b8cc20363185","tid":1999691,"uid":185416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:51:42.000Z","msg":"李文亮"},{"pid":"b640ee5724820a78695f3f2d78078f442da4c1f5","tid":1999691,"uid":269202,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T10:53:16.000Z","msg":"單純樓主..."},{"pid":"9b4ecbfab7da64765c8abebc26fdbdb43ad33f7e","tid":1999691,"uid":185416,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"